{
  "stem": "27409.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We came to my aunt, one of my aunt, which lived in this city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "She has a large flat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So we were my grandfather, my step grandmother, my eldest uncle with his five married [? son ?] with the wife, the younger son.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It was our-- our family, we four, a cousin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We were full there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We slept out on the floor, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we [? what ?]had we had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Because when we went, we took what we could take on the-- we were permitted only entering to the ghetto-- not to go out again.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We saved what we could save, food and this, and we brought it in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There you could move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "You [? really ?] had to give up the keys with the address [INAUDIBLE] of your flat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "It all was taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "You can imagine my parents, after so many years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "They married in 1919.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "The had to go out of their home, which they had all collected and [? homeless, ?] and this for [? nothing ?] with a-- a rucksack-- not a rucksack, a bag.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And we stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Then came the order of deportation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Officially, it was for colonization Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "They told now population [? the ?] Ukraine, the Russian have taken off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "You will have to colonize and work there, agriculture.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And the SS started [? commanding ?] [? around. ?] They were SS officer and Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "We had to go ourselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And there were street after street, and they were always reducing the area of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "You had to walk yourself to the [? umliegeplatz. ?] It was in the station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "They had put us in trains, not [INAUDIBLE] only.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "They were [? good stays. ?] The windows, the small windows, were barred with barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
